summary: An Ordinance appropriating the sum of Eleven Thousand Four Hundred Seventy and 44/100 (11,470.44) Dollars, or so much thereof as may be necessary from the General Fund of the City of Seattle, to be pay the City's portion of the cost of the improvement of Jackson Street, et al, by paving the same, under Ordinance No. 19837, creating Local Improvement District No. 1919.
